{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "孙剑接到老伯紧急召集讯号后快马赶回，途中从犬组成员处得知有人想杀老伯，在路上截住了逃亡的小何并将其打成重伤。老伯看到万鹏王送来的四口箱子——装着文虎、文豹、武老刀的尸体和小武的残躯——判断万鹏王即将全面进攻，而刺杀小何的幕后黑手并非万鹏王。孙剑自作聪明抓回小何反而打草惊蛇，老伯虽痛失爱子线索但冷静应对，命律香川追查幕后主使，同时在铁成刚兄弟大祭之日设下埋伏。祭坛上铁成刚当众自刎殉义，混入吊唁人群中的万鹏王手下突袭孙剑，孙剑以刚猛拳法击退敌人，但被藏在棺材中的刺客用毒香迷倒后一剑穿胸而死。老伯痛失独子，悲恸之下命令去找韩棠。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_nv_zi_1",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_zi_1",
      "speaker_name": "女子",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "怎么？你这就想走了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_zi_1",
      "speaker_name": "女子",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "你舍得走？就算你舍得走，我也不放你走。",
      "tone": "纠缠",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_quan_zu_yuan",
      "text": "你盯的是谁？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_he",
      "text": "我姓孙，叫孙剑！",
      "tone": "威吓",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已将这人抓回来了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "你在哪里找到他的？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "路上。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "路上有很多人，你为什么不一个个全都抓回来？",
      "tone": "冷讽",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "我知道这人想害你，而且是从这里逃出去的。",
      "tone": "辩解",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "有人告诉我。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "我只问你，有谁从这里逃出去过没有？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "假如真有人从这里逃出去，会是个怎么样的人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "当然是个极厉害的角色。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "像那样厉害的角色，你有本事一拳将他击倒？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "他这件事做得虽愚蠢，但却不能说完全没有用。",
      "tone": "评价",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wu",
      "text": "我一定替你报仇。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "他至少能证明这姓何的绝不是万鹏王派来的。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "万鹏王现在已指着我的鼻子叫阵，这人若是他派来的，他用不着杀人灭口。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "我们本来是可以查出那人的，只可惜",
      "tone": "遗憾",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "只可惜有人自作聪明，误了大事。",
      "tone": "严厉",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "我们慢慢还是可以查出那个人是谁的。",
      "tone": "安慰",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "那是以后的事，现在我们要将全部力量都用来对付万鹏王！",
      "tone": "决断",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "我去！",
      "tone": "激昂",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "去干什么？他正坐在家里等你去送死！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "他要我们去，我们就偏不去，他能等，我们就得比他更能等，他若想再激怒我们，就必定还会有所行动。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "服从",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你想他下次行动是什么？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "明天，是铁成刚为他的兄弟大祭之日，万鹏王认为我们必定有人到山上去祭奠，必定准备在那里有所行动，可是我们就一定要他扑个空。",
      "tone": "谋略",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你在山上已完全布置好了么？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "抬棺的、挖坟的、吹鼓手、念经的道士，都完全换上我们的人，现在我们别的不怕，就怕万鹏王不动。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "孙剑一定会有法子要他动的。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "他们看到孙剑在那里，也非动不可。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "这次万鹏王还不至于亲自出手，所以我也准备不露面。",
      "tone": "谋略",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "我想去看看。",
      "tone": "主动",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你不能去，他们只要看到你，就必定会猜出我们已有预防，何况",
      "tone": "断然",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你还有别的事做。",
      "tone": "指示",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "服从",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "万鹏王由我来对付，你全力追查谁是主使他的人，无论你用什么法子，却千万不可被第三个人知道。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "只要这人不死，我就有法子。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "我当然绝不会让他死的。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "铁成刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的兄弟惨遭杀害，而且还蒙冤名，我却逃了，就像是一条狗似的逃了。",
      "tone": "悲愤",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "铁成刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我逃，并不是怕死，而是要等到今天，今天他们的冤名洗刷，我已没有再活下去的理由",
      "tone": "决绝",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_ren_1",
      "speaker_name": "无名人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "注意右臂的麻布。",
      "tone": "高声",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_ren_1",
      "speaker_name": "跪地者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是，我不是他们一伙的",
      "tone": "哭求",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "挥刀者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死就死，没有什么了不起。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "挥刀者",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "我想死都不行？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_ren_2",
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_ren_2",
      "speaker_name": "挥刀者",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "你想怎么样？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "带这人回去，告诉万鹏王，他怎样对付我们，我们必将加十倍还给他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去找韩棠！",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 8
    }
  ],
